data.description:
Stunning mountain home nestled in the heart of Waynesville, NC.! This 2-bedroom, 2-bath sanctuary offers breathtaking long-range views of surrounding mountains and the serene Lake Junaluska. 
Inside is a world of comfort and style. One bedroom/full updated bath on each level allow for privacy and convenience. Hardwood flooring throughout the home adds a touch of warmth; the 2 stone fireplaces create a cozy atmosphere. A well-appointed kitchen has ample counter space and seamlessly flows into the dining room/living area, floor-to-ceiling windows offer panoramic views of mountains and Lake Junaluska. On the lower level this floor plan repeats itself with a bar & family room accompanied by the second fireplace, a covered patio, and hot tub. 
A detached heated garage is adjacent to a versatile room currently used as a pottery studio with its own full bath.
Updates: roof (2019), mini-split system (2022), freshly painted interior and exterior, & more.
TAX RECORDS INCORRECT. NO DRIVE BYS.
